---
/**
 * DivisionsIntro - a quiet, non-interactive paragraph-style introduction
 * to the three divisions. Sits between the hero and the first deep
 * DivisionPanel below. Its job is purely orientation: tell the visitor
 * what Teaching/Research/Innovation mean before they meet them in
 * depth. No clicks, no CTAs - that work is happening in the panels
 * below.
 */
---

<section class="dvi" aria-labelledby="dvi-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="dvi-grid" data-reveal>
      <div class="dvi-head">
        <p class="mono dvi-eyebrow">How the work fits together</p>
        <h2 class="dvi-title" id="dvi-heading">
          The organisation is organised in <span class="dvi-em">three divisions.</span>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="dvi-body">
        <ul class="dvi-list">
          <li class="dvi-row">
            <span class="dvi-marker dvi-marker-teaching" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <p class="dvi-text">
              <strong class="dvi-name dvi-name-teaching">Teaching</strong>
              <span class="dvi-sep" aria-hidden="true">-</span>
              building the people. Structured cohorts and a community that learns together.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li class="dvi-row">
            <span class="dvi-marker dvi-marker-research" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <p class="dvi-text">
              <strong class="dvi-name dvi-name-research">Research</strong>
              <span class="dvi-sep" aria-hidden="true">-</span>
              building the knowledge. Open datasets, models, and benchmarks the field is missing for African contexts.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li class="dvi-row">
            <span class="dvi-marker dvi-marker-innovation" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <p class="dvi-text">
              <strong class="dvi-name dvi-name-innovation">Innovation</strong>
              <span class="dvi-sep" aria-hidden="true">-</span>
              shipping the work. Turning what's been learned and researched into products that work in the world.
            </p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .dvi {
    padding-block: clamp(56px, 7vw, 88px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .dvi-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(0, 1.4fr);
    gap: clamp(40px, 6vw, 88px);
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .dvi-eyebrow {
    color: var(--gold-deep);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  [data-theme='dark'] .dvi-eyebrow { color: var(--gold); }
  .dvi-title {
    font-size: var(--t-display-m);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--ink);
    max-width: 16ch;
  }
  .dvi-em {
    display: inline-block;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.78em;
    color: var(--gold-deep);
    margin-top: 4px;
  }
  [data-theme='dark'] .dvi-em { color: var(--gold); }

  .dvi-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .dvi-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 18px;
    padding-block: 22px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .dvi-row:first-child { padding-top: 0; }
  .dvi-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; padding-bottom: 0; }

  .dvi-marker {
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 9px;
  }
  .dvi-marker-teaching { background: var(--teaching); }
  .dvi-marker-research { background: var(--research-text); }
  .dvi-marker-innovation { background: var(--innovation); }

  .dvi-text {
    font-size: 16.5px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--ink-mid);
    margin: 0;
  }
  .dvi-name {
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .dvi-name-teaching { color: var(--teaching); }
  .dvi-name-research { color: var(--ink); }
  [data-theme='dark'] .dvi-name-research { color: var(--research-text); }
  .dvi-name-innovation { color: var(--innovation); }
  .dvi-sep {
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    margin-inline: 8px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 880px) {
    .dvi-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 32px;
    }
    .dvi-title { max-width: none; }
  }
</style>
